subtitleNullable: This dataset shows all of the chapters in the Berserk manga series
descriptionNullable:
This dataset shows all of the chapters in the Berserk manga series. The Excel file includes filters for each column.

**Column Description**

- **N°**: Chapter number
- **Chapter**: Chapter name in English
- **Japanese**: Chapter name in Japanese
- **Hepburn**: Hepburn romanization of the name in Japanese
- **N° Pages**: Number of pages of the chapter
- **Volume**: Volume to which the chapter belongs
- **Arc**: Arc to which the chapter belongs
- **Publication**: Original date of publication

**NOTE**: The first 16 chapters correspond to the prelude of Berserk before the actual chapter count begins.
